Package org.openlca.jsonld

Class MemStore

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.jsonld.MemStore
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, EntityStore
public class MemStore extends Object implements EntityStore
A simple implementation of the EntityStore interface that stores the JSON objects in memory. Not all features of a real file based entity store are supported.

    • getBinFiles

      public List<String> getBinFiles​(ModelType type, String id)
      Description copied from interface: EntityStore
      Returns a list of paths to external (binary) files for a model with the given type and ID. The returned paths should be directly resolvable so that a call get(path) on this entity store returns the binary data of this file. If there are no external files available an empty list should be returned.
      Specified by:
      getBinFiles in interface EntityStore
